{"tid":1173611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[食鹽多過食米] 俄保母以50克鹽混粥　迫2歲童食到鹽中毒鹹死　謀殺罪成囚14年","createTime":"2019-05-27T08:41:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T08:52:14.000Z","uid":1735,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ae697f09f5b2571a0808467c42cebdf237ef6000","tid":1173611,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T08:41:46.000Z","msg":"孩子總會哭鬧，絕不應殘忍對待！俄羅斯一名本身育有一對子女的25歲保母去年6月因不滿一名由她看管的2歲男童不停哭鬧，竟在粥內混入最少50克鹽，然後迫男童吃下以元懲罰，這種不會造成表面傷痕的做法，卻令男童因鹽中毒死亡，保母被控謀殺罪。案件早前審理完畢，保母謀殺罪成，監禁14年。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3W56aWL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3W56aWL.png&h=911cb898&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事件發生於俄羅斯西北部阿爾漢格爾斯克州（Arkhangelsk Oblast）的霍爾姆戈里（Kholmogory）一條小村莊內，犯人為25歲的保母黛安殊（Yana Deinesh），她本身亦育有2名子女，去年6月照顧一名2歲男童的時候，因為不滿男童不斷哭鬧，加上黛安殊心情不佳，認為應對男童懲罰一下。<br />\n<br />\n黛安殊將一大包鹽加到男童正在進食的粥內，攪拌之後再強迫男童將所有粥都吃下。男童被迫吃鹹粥後感不適，其後更失去意識，送院急救後再被送到深切治療部，最終仍然因鹽中毒而不治。調查人員表示，男童被迫吃下的鹽至少有50克，令其體內鹽份較正常水平超出60倍而致命。<br />\n<br />\n黛安殊被捕後承認罪行，但稱沒有想過會造成這樣的結果，強調完全沒有想過要殺死男童，但她終被判謀殺罪成，判監14年。<br />\n<br />\n（The Sun、New York Post）"},{"pid":"b086c061490bcc93c481cb850f0c3086895b37c7","tid":1173611,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T08:42:37.000Z","msg":"鹹濕保母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c67eebdab7c15615b2f686d93bcabf9ed83d140","tid":1173611,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b086c061490bcc93c481cb850f0c3086895b37c7","tid":1173611,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T08:42:37.000Z","msg":"鹹濕保母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T08:45:12.000Z","msg":"賤乜乜,但我講唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5902404772d74d5d5f4fca777ddd231109cb1d39","tid":1173611,"uid":156376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T08:47:05.000Z","msg":"好撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb671e3b0cd585e5b99dbf5b05d842106e2e2cb","tid":1173611,"uid":76314,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T08:50:09.000Z","msg":"bb喊就一定㗎啦，唔係請你返嚟做保母把撚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自己有小朋友都落到手，毒死人地個小朋友咁閪仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc59d80a2b9ed8bb3dc63157508bab74130bb199","tid":1173611,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T08:52:14.000Z","msg":"唔鍾意細路就咪撚生仔同做保母啦"}]}